<emphasis bold="true" box="[288,520,1935,1959]" italics="true" pageId="10" pageNumber="483">Eccoptolonthus ernsti</emphasis>
(
<bibRefCitation author="Schillhammer, H." box="[537,755,1935,1959]" pageId="10" pageNumber="483" pagination="133 - 163" refId="ref16374" refString="Schillhammer, H. (2011) Old and new Staphylinini from the Palearctic and Oriental Regions (Coleoptera: Staphylinidae: Staphylininae). Koleopterologische Rundschau, 81, 133 - 163." type="journal article" year="2011">Schillhammer, 2011</bibRefCitation>
