A. aedeagus, dorsal (parameral side) view; B. aedeagus, lateral view; C. sternite IX of male; D. tergite X of male; E. sternite VIII of male; F. stylus of tergite IX of male. Scale bars, A, B= 0.18 mm; C, F= 0.24 mm; D= 0.2 mm; E= 0.36 mm.
